Later, an officer comes to inquire the background and decide whether to issue him an election ticket or not. Last but not the least, the great singer Gurdaas Maan joins Kapil on the stage to promote his forthcoming movie - Dil Vil Pyaar Vyaar. Watch the episode and have a blast.
